snippet.title: KIM THE AVENGER COW
snippet.description: An accident was bound to happen so Kim The Avenger Cow could exist. Her mission is to make us look in the mirror and see the monsters we have become. We aren't the only specie in this planet! We don't own the lives of every creature in the planet so we can turn them into profit! Watch out! Kim has a message and we won't like her way to deliver it.
